<figureCitation id="25C501D03F752712D7085A9CCAEC5ED5" box="[329,447,1942,1965]" captionStart="FIGURES 6 – 12" captionStartId="2.[151,258,1537,1559]" captionTargetBox="[150,1436,191,1505]" captionTargetId="figure@2.[150,1436,191,1515]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURES 6 – 12. Brevivalvala melanosticta sp. nov. 6. Male pygofer side, lateral view; 7. Valve and subgenital plate, ventral view; 8. Style, dorsal view; 9. Aedeagus, ventral view; 10. Aedeagus, lateral view; 11. Connective, dorsal view; 12. Profemur and protibial, anterior view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/259706/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="82">
